thread.title: Jamel Wright

author: Jamel Wright
title: Jamel Wright
text: I ordered an engagement ring from them. They were great from the moment I ordered. I was actually off in the ring size and had to call to make an adjustment, which was hassle free. There were no delays in my order and it arrived on time, which was a shocker since they make the jewelry custom to order. There's no doubt that I will be recommending them to my friends and will certainly use them again.
